title: Seo Ji-soo
summary: Seo Ji-soo (born 21 May 1985) is a former professional StarCraft player from South Korea who played under the alias ToSsGirL (Terran, STX Soul) and referred to as the "Queen of Terran". On, 17 July 2012, Seo Ji-soo officially retired from pro gaming and she is now running a cybermall called 'tossgirl'.
